  "longDescription": "Make every day epic with Samsung Galaxy S24.<br><br>\\nSee a delicious-looking dish on your social feed but don’t see a recipe?\\nSimply Circle to Search<sup>2</sup> with Google to find it in seconds. Then head to a\\nsunny farmer’s market to pick up the ingredients and see your list clearly\\non the bright, adaptive display of Samsung Galaxy S24.<br><br>\\nOnce the meal is ready, capture stunning close-ups of your dish and dinner guests, no matter the lighting, with a high-res camera and Nightography. And all the while, you can stay plugged into the moment, not the outlet, with a long-lasting battery.<br><br>\\nDo more easily with Samsung Galaxy S24. Epic, just like that.\\n<br><br>\\nCheck out our <a href=\\\"https://www.t-mobile.com/offers/samsung-phone-deals?icid=MGPO_TMO_U_24SMGXYNPI_C8816AC1ACE23BCB37641\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">latest Samsung deals</a> on the newest Galaxy phones, <a href=\\\"https://www.t-mobile.com/tablets/brand/samsung\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">tablets<a/>, and <a href=\\\"https://www.t-mobile.com/smart-watches/brand/samsung\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">watches</a>, and get the scoop on the latest Samsung phones. Also, be sure to explore the awesome new Samsung <a href=\\\"https://www.t-mobile.com/cell-phone/samsung-galaxy-s24-plus?icid=MGPO_TMO_U_24SMGXYNPI_C8816AC1ACE23BCB37627\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Galaxy S24+</a>, and <a href=\\\"https://www.t-mobile.com/cell-phone/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra?icid=MGPO_TMO_U_24SMGXYNPI_C8816AC1ACE23BCB37634\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Galaxy S24 Ultra</a> powered by our largest and fastest 5G Network.<br><br>\\n \\nNeed help choosing your next Galaxy phone? Check out our complete guide on choosing the <a href=\\\"https://www.t-mobile.com/news/devices/best-samsung-galaxy-phones\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">best Samsung Galaxy phone in 2024</a>.\\n<br><br>\\n\\n<small>\\n<sup>1</sup>As compared to Galaxy S23 and S23+.<br>\\n<sup>2</sup>Requires internet connection; results may vary by uniqueness, clarity and\\nframing of circled image and related factors.</small>\\n<br><br><b>Samsung Galaxy S24 Quick Facts</b> \\n<ul>\\n<li>When was the Samsung Galaxy S24 be released? The Galaxy S24 was released on January 31, 2024.\\n<li>What colors are available for the Samsung Galaxy S24? The Galaxy S24 is available in 4 colors: Amber Yellow, Cobalt Violet, Marble Gray, and Onyx Black*.\\n<li>What are the storage options for the Samsung Galaxy S24? The Galaxy S24 has 2 memory storage sizes: 128GB and 256GB.\\n<li>Is the Samsung Galaxy S24 phone waterproof/water resistant? This phone is IPx8 Water Resistant.\\n<li>Does the Samsung Galaxy S24 have a SD card slot? There is no option for expandable memory.\\n<li>Does this phone have a headphone jack? No, the Samsung Galaxy S24 does not have a headphone jack.\\n<li>Does the Samsung Galaxy S24 have or come with a stylus? No, this phone is not compatible.</ul> <small><sup>*</sup>Color and memory size options may vary in availability online or in store.</small><br><br>\\n\\n<div style=\\\"height: 0px; overflow: hidden; padding-top: 56.25%; position: relative; width: 100%;\\\"> <iframe style=\\\"position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; width: 80%; height: 80%;\\\" src=\\\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/7yFH42YRjs0\\\" title=\\\"Samsung Spring Launch 2024 | T-Mobile\\\" frameBorder=\\\"0\\\" allow=\\\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\\\" allowFullScreen></iframe></div>",
